<i>911 operator. what's your emergency?</i>

510
01:12:55.918 --> 01:12:57.178
I need help.

511
01:13:00.715 --> 01:13:01.810
<i>Ma'am?</i>

512
01:13:02.028 --> 01:13:04.560
<i>Ma'am. are you there? Ma'am?</i>

513
01:13:05.875 --> 01:13:07.144
<i>Ma'am. we're here with you.</i>

514
01:13:07.201 --> 01:13:09.294
<i>We're keeping the line open.
we're gonna get you some help.</i>

515
01:13:09.357 --> 01:13:10.464
<i>Do not hang up.</i>

516
01:13:10.529 --> 01:13:13.065
<i>I'm gonna place you on hold
while we triangulate your location.</i>

517
01:13:13.142 --> 01:13:14.932
<i>I'll be right back with you.</i>

518
01:13:40.255 --> 01:13:42.154
<i>Ma'am. I'm back. Is it safe to talk?</i>

519
01:13:42.231 --> 01:13:45.095
- What is your emergency?
- My son has been kidnapped.

520
01:13:45.338 --> 01:13:47.588
And I'm in the house where I think
they're keeping him.

521
01:13:47.725 --> 01:13:50.244
<i>We think we found you.
Can you verified your address?</i>

522
01:13:50.325 --> 01:13:52.525
Yes. 125. route 77.

523
01:13:52.794 --> 01:13:55.664
<i>And do you know if there's anyone else
in the house with you. ma'am?</i>

524
01:13:56.542 --> 01:13:57.941
I don't know. I'm not sure. but...

525
01:13:57.989 --> 01:14:02.700
But the woman that took him is out
in a barn or some house.

526
01:14:02.748 --> 01:14:03.801
It's near where I am.

527
01:14:03.849 --> 01:14:05.575
<i>I've already contacted
the dispatch officers.</i>

528
01:14:05.623 --> 01:14:06.551
<i>They're on the way.</i>

529
01:14:06.599 --> 01:14:08.598
<i>You need to find a safe place
to wait until they're arrive.</i>

530
01:14:08.646 --> 01:14:10.232
Okay. 
How long is that gonna take?

531
01:14:10.289 --> 01:14:11.623
<i>They'll be there very soon.</i>

532
01:14:11.671 --> 01:14:13.466
<i>I just need you to stay
on the line with me. okay?</i>

533
01:14:13.514 --> 01:14:14.286
Okay.

534
01:14:14.334 --> 01:14:17.318
- Is that gonna be like 5 minutes?
- Between 7-15 minutes. ma'am.

535
01:14:17.372 --> 01:14:20.005
Oh. God. 15 minutes...
That's a long time.

536
01:14:20.084 --> 01:14:21.942
<i>It's alright. ma'am.
The police are on their way.</i>

537
01:14:21.990 --> 01:14:25.826
<i>I need you to get to a safe place.
stay here on the line with me now. okay?</i>

538
01:14:28.209 --> 01:14:30.787
<i>Would you let me know when
you find a safe place to hide?</i>

539
01:14:31.495 --> 01:14:32.975
<i>Ma'am. are you there?</i>

540
01:14:33.505 --> 01:14:36.834
- Ma'am? Ma'am?
- Hang up. hang up.

541
01:14:38.154 --> 01:14:39.378
Oh. God.

542
01:14:46.093 --> 01:14:47.558
Terry!

543
01:14:49.398 --> 01:14:51.618
Terry. are you back?

544
01:14:53.757 --> 01:14:56.538
Terry. was that you on the phone?

545
01:14:58.665 --> 01:15:00.156
Terry!

546
01:15:18.842 --> 01:15:20.445
Terry!

547
01:16:14.288 --> 01:16:15.850
Frankie.

548
01:17:43.735 --> 01:17:45.141
Frankie?

549
01:17:50.165 --> 01:17:51.525
<i>Mommy?</i>

550
01:17:52.495 --> 01:17:53.719
Frankie?

551
01:17:54.443 --> 01:17:56.083
<i>Mommy?</i>

552
01:17:56.492 --> 01:17:58.162
Where are you. sweetheart?

553
01:17:58.375 --> 01:17:59.700
Frankie.

554
01:18:00.585 --> 01:18:03.403
- Where are you. honey?
- Up here.

555
01:18:04.315 --> 01:18:06.985
Mommy. mommy.

556
01:18:07.305 --> 01:18:08.934
- Hi. sweetheart.
- I'm scared.

557
01:18:09.014 --> 01:18:11.027
- Where have you been?
- Yes. I'm gonna get you down.

558
01:18:11.147 --> 01:18:12.645
I'm gonna get you down. honey.

559
01:18:12.733 --> 01:18:14.845
<i>Are you the police?</i>

560
01:18:16.895 --> 01:18:18.024
What is that. Frankie?

561
01:18:18.100 --> 01:18:20.912
- I'm Lucy.
- I'm Libby.

562
01:18:20.997 --> 01:18:23.345
Oh!
Oh my God. there's...

563
01:18:23.393 --> 01:18:25.145
There's three of you up there.

564
01:18:25.305 --> 01:18:27.920
- Mommy. give me a help.
- Okay. honey. look...

565
01:18:28.034 --> 01:18:30.483
I'm gonna get you down. okay?

566
01:18:30.610 --> 01:18:33.044
- Come up the ladder.
- I can't.

567
01:18:33.201 --> 01:18:36.302
I can't. honey.
because the ladder is locked.

568
01:18:36.560 --> 01:18:40.162
So you're gonna have to come down
through this hole.

569
01:18:40.435 --> 01:18:42.594
But first I'm gonna have to get...
No. no. Frankie. don't.

570
01:18:42.655 --> 01:18:45.884
No. don't put your legs down. honey.
You can't fit through there.

571
01:18:45.975 --> 01:18:49.061
- No. just wait a second.
- Grab me.

572
01:18:49.165 --> 01:18:52.123
Put your legs up. Frankie.
so mommy can hit with the shovel.

573
01:18:52.195 --> 01:18:54.585
- Put your legs...
- Grab me.

574
01:18:54.632 --> 01:18:58.062
♪♪

575
01:18:58.290 --> 01:19:02.082
Okay. Frankie. listen.
I'm gonna be right back. okay?

576
01:19:02.175 --> 01:19:04.925
- No. mommy. wait!
- You wait right there.

577
01:19:04.972 --> 01:19:08.517
♪♪

578
01:19:08.564 --> 01:19:12.374
♪♪

579
01:19:12.421 --> 01:19:16.397
♪♪

580
01:19:18.604 --> 01:19:22.047
Frankie. Frankie. put your legs
back up in that hole. okay?

581
01:19:22.095 --> 01:19:23.218
We're gonna have to go fast.

582
01:19:23.266 --> 01:19:25.604
Get your legs back up in that hole.
Frankie. right now!

583
01:19:25.667 --> 01:19:27.720
- Mommy. mommy...
- Frankie!

584
01:19:48.806 --> 01:19:52.298
Okay. Okay. come on. Frankie.
Come on.

585
01:20:04.815 --> 01:20:07.204
- Come on. girls. Come on.
- No. I'm scared.

586
01:20:07.268 --> 01:20:10.135
- Come on. you have to come down.
- I want my mommy.

587
01:20:10.229 --> 01:20:13.479
Okay. okay. okay.

588
01:20:13.846 --> 01:20:16.190
We're gonna play the quiet game. okay?

589
01:20:16.377 --> 01:20:19.649
I need both of you to be very quiet.
don't make a sound. okay?

590
01:20:19.697 --> 01:20:22.515
I'm gonna come back.
I'm gonna come back for you. okay?

591
01:20:24.755 --> 01:20:27.440
Go get her! Get her!

592
01:20:28.396 --> 01:20:29.815
Come on.

593
01:20:30.253 --> 01:20:31.727
Come on.

594
01:20:37.127 --> 01:20:40.010
Okay. Frankie. 
we're gonna have to hide.

595
01:24:30.455 --> 01:24:32.275
You sit right here. okay?

596
01:24:33.405 --> 01:24:35.395
I'm gonna go get the girls. okay?

597
01:24:35.687 --> 01:24:37.207
We'll get them out of here.

598
01:24:39.720 --> 01:24:42.955
Hi. you guys. I'm back.

599
01:24:43.335 --> 01:24:46.464
- Come on. it's time to come down now.
- I want my mommy.

600
01:24:46.534 --> 01:24:48.224
It's okay. sweetheart.
Come on down.

601
01:24:48.343 --> 01:24:51.298
Come on. honey. I'm here to help you.
It's okay.

602
01:24:54.145 --> 01:24:55.905
What the hell is going on here?

603
01:24:56.262 --> 01:24:57.872
Who the hell are you?

604
01:25:00.425 --> 01:25:02.314
- Who are you?
- I live next door.

605
01:25:02.361 --> 01:25:03.901
I heard gunshots.

606
01:25:04.875 --> 01:25:06.305
Where's Margo?

607
01:25:07.915 --> 01:25:10.146
- In the water.
- What?

608
01:25:10.403 --> 01:25:11.747
Yeah.

609
01:25:12.535 --> 01:25:14.759
She and her husband kidnapped my son.

610
01:25:15.195 --> 01:25:18.509
I've lived next to the Vicky's
for 14 years.

611
01:25:19.363 --> 01:25:21.931
They ain't kidnappers.
You turn around.

612
01:25:26.429 --> 01:25:28.626
I called the police. you know.

613
01:25:30.017 --> 01:25:34.322
- Who's up there?
- Those are kids. More abducted kids.

614
01:25:35.095 --> 01:25:37.970
Yeah. they're up there in that hole.

615
01:25:41.905 --> 01:25:43.646
Dear Lord.

616
01:25:45.059 --> 01:25:46.552
We have to get them down.

617
01:25:47.135 --> 01:25:48.365
Hey. you two.

618
01:25:48.861 --> 01:25:51.205
We're gonna get you down
from there right now.

619
01:25:51.255 --> 01:25:55.364
- I wanna go home!
- We are gonna go home right now.

620
01:25:55.474 --> 01:25:56.874
Both of you.

621
01:25:58.677 --> 01:26:00.123
Just come to the opening.

622
01:26:00.638 --> 01:26:02.178
Come on. girls.

623
01:26:02.709 --> 01:26:03.754
Come on.

624
01:26:04.083 --> 01:26:07.036
Wait a minute.
I never told you how many.

625
01:26:09.144 --> 01:26:12.064
And I never told you they were girls.

626
01:26:26.978 --> 01:26:29.748
You took the wrong kid.

627
01:26:50.605 --> 01:26:52.355
Oh. sweetheart...

628
01:27:46.255 --> 01:27:48.863
<i>This is Julian Buescher with
an unbelievable story...</i>

629
01:27:48.949 --> 01:27:50.839
<i>breaking out of
Jefferson Parish right now.</i>

630
01:27:50.887 --> 01:27:53.449
<i>Three suspected
child abductor are dead...</i>

631
01:27:53.535 --> 01:27:55.754
<i>and a woman is reunited
with her son tonight.</i>

632
01:27:55.809 --> 01:27:59.049
<i>After what police called it
an unprecedented civilian pursuit.</i>

633
01:27:59.119 --> 01:28:03.138
<i>Amazingly. the mother got into her
own vehicle and chase the suspects.</i>

634
01:28:03.437 --> 01:28:05.116
<i>A police spokesman has confirmed...</i>

635
01:28:05.171 --> 01:28:08.018
<i>the break of an overseas
child abduction ring.</i>

636
01:28:08.390 --> 01:28:12.912
<i>Arrests has been made in Paris.
New York. London and Dubai.</i>

637
01:28:13.249 --> 01:28:16.476
<i>This mother is one incredible hero.</i>

